In 2026, the best value on the Blue Nile site isn't actually a Blue Nile branded product. Following the Signet merger, Blue Nile now lists **[James Allen Lab-Grown inventory](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/by-james-allen?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)**.

The _Flower Clasp Tennis Bracelet With 5 CTW Lab-Grown Diamonds_ at **$2,835** is a James Allen piece. It uses 14K gold and high-fire lab stones. It is the gold standard for "Value Arbitrage" right now.

